# Project-specific ignores only.
# Universal ignores (node_modules, .env*, logs, OS junk, editor/agent files,
# .vercel, coverage, generic build outputs) live in ~/.gitignore_global —
# see Hubspot Development - Personal/CLAUDE.md §12.

# Next.js
.next/
next-env.d.ts.backup

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

# PEM / certs — Next's default scaffold ignores these; keeping project-local
# since PEMs aren't universal ignore-territory.
*.pem

.vercel
.env*.local
